Dominique Davray https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dominique_Davray 0 Dominique Davray (born Marie-Louise Gournay; 27 January 1919 in Paris – 16 August 1998 in Paris) was a French actress. She performed in more than ninety films from 1942 to 1983. Dominique_Davray ( born Marie-Louise_Gournay ; 27_January_1919 in Paris – 16_August_1998 in Paris ) was a_French_actress . She performed in more_than_ninety_films from 1942 to 1983 .
